data.description: If you have a discriminating buyer looking for excellence, look no further! This total 3 bed 2.5 bath 2 car garage remodel was completed by the utmost professional with attention to each and every detail. The paint color, tile choices, stainless steel appliances, updated light fixtures, total bath remodels and granite have brought this home up to date for 2023 like no other. As you walk up to the front door you will appreciate the drive up appeal to this home along with the new front door featuring dual side windows. As you enter the home, the towering ceilings and ceiling beams just make the room feel elegant. As you step down from the living area you will walk into the formal dining area right off the kitchen, which is perfect for entertaining. The chef in the family will enjoy cooking with stainless steel appliances, oversized pantry and plenty of granite countertop room for serving guests. Outside you will enjoy a fenced rear yard, concrete patio and storage shed or workshop.
